  "texts": [
    "Search strategyAs shown in Figure 3, the search strategy begins with selecting a digital library.",
    "We chose IEEExplore, ACM, Springer, and ScienceDirect digital libraries.",
    "Explore and ACM are the main choices because they are scientific associations with a high reputation in computers and information technology.",
    "Both associations are also publishers of reputable scientific journals.",
    "Meanwhile, Springer and ScienceDirect were chosen because they are publishers of scientific journals with a good reputation among scholars."
  ]
}